==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfraught
<hw>Un*fraught"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>fraught</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not fraught; not
burdened.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[1st pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>fraught</ets>.]</ety> <def>Removed, as a burden; unloaded.</def>
<rj><au>P. Fletcher.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfree</ent>⟦br⟧
